{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":25945,"duration_api_ms":24594,"ttft_ms":12049,"num_turns":3,"result":"CLI が `should_stop=true` / `blocking_reasons: [\"dirty_or_stale_source\"]` を返しました。Agentic Search はここで停止します。\n\n---\n\n## CLI ブロック通知\n\n**理由:** `dirty_or_stale_source` — Source Specs のインデックスが古い（またはダーティ）な状態です。\n\n**CLIの推奨アクション:**\n\n```\nrun /spec-core before /spec-inject\n```\n\n---\n\n## 復旧手順\n\n`/spec-inject` を実行する前に、まず `/spec-core` を実行してインデックスを最新状態に更新してください。\n\n```\n/spec-core\n```\n\n`/spec-core` 完了後、再度 `/spec-inject 認証とセッションに関する制約を確認して` を実行していただければ、Agentic Search を再開して制約を抽出します。\n\n---\n\n**注記:** CLI の診断情報では `docs/spec/auth.md` 配下に以下のセクションが認識されているため、`/spec-core` 後はこれらが主な探索対象になります:\n- `#0001-authentication-specification`\n- `#0002-session-management`\n- `#0003-csrf-protection`\n- `#0004-authorization`","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"feac97a9-23d7-4756-ac82-2bdbebab815b","total_cost_usd":0.08116875,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14541,"cache_read_input_tokens":39010,"output_tokens":995,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":14541,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":348,"cache_read_input_tokens":25540,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2471,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2471},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":4,"outputTokens":995,"cacheReadInputTokens":39010,"cacheCreationInputTokens":14541,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.08116875,"contextWindow":400000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"f40d1211-1945-4790-b36d-adc3a8d8b942"}
